Huh. I didn't find it sue-ish at all, nor a parody of one. Frankly, I don't think it has anything to do at all with Mary-Sues. It's a mimic with a need to be admired.

The reason its requests are granted is because it's completely harmless, unless you count damage to your ego. Keep it away from the outside world and nothing bad can possibly happen.

I'd downgrade that sentence to "may be granted", though. I suppose it could turn violent if we deny all its requests, and it's nice to have something that doesn't require blast doors and passcode entry, but we don't need to appease it.







