This particular SCP manages to annoy the living hell out of me. It's one thing: better than you. For any value of you, nonetheless. It's absurdly dangerous, as well. Remind me WHY this is only classed Euclid? It's got the potential to be exceedingly dangerous. Yes, I know that it's the Contain part that comes in here, since you CAN contain it By being subservient to it. Really? It rubs me entirely the wrong way, for personal reasons. Makes me uncomfortable. Now, when I imagine myself in the containment group for this SCP, it makes me wanna kill myself. No matter what I can do, it can do better. Always. And you can't do shit about it. I think it would be very, very bad for morale at the very least. But eh, this might just be my inferiority complex speaking. That's also the reason I'm not downvoting it. That, and since I'm a newb here, so my voice counts for about less than nothing.







